This video demonstrates the full execution of the n8n workflow for the AI Video Ad Generator project.

The workflow performs:

- Product research using Tavily
- ICP and pain point research
- AI generated ad hooks and ideas
- AI storyboard creation
- Automatic scene breakdown
- Video generation using HeyGen API
- Scene stitching
- Google Drive storage
- Logging results to Google Sheets

